OL,4,Cburning flat jailed
OL,6,FA killer who fatally attacked a man
OL,7,Fbefore leaving him lifeless in a
OL,8,Fburning flat has been jailed for life.
OL,10,FMark Vaskouski, 27, severely beat
OL,11,FAnthony Ibbitson at his home on Terry
OL,12,FStreet in Hull after demanding drugs
OL,13,Fand cash on 29 November last year.
OL,15,FA court heard how he then fled, as
OL,16,Ffire engulfed the property, shouting:
OL,17,F"Enjoy the fire."
