OL,3,CKiller who left victim to die in
OL,4,Cburning flat jailed
OL,6,FThe fire is thought to have been
OL,7,Fcaused by a candle as Mr Ibbitson, 54,
OL,8,Fattempted to heat his home after his
OL,9,Felectricity was cut off.
OL,11,FMr Ibbitson, who suffered serious
OL,12,Finjuries to his face, neck and head,
OL,13,Fwas left defenceless and unable to
OL,14,Fleave the property. He was rescued by
OL,15,Ffirefighters and taken first to Hull
OL,16,FRoyal Infirmary and then to
OL,17,FPinderfields Hospital, Wakefield.
OL,19,FHe had burns to more than a third of
OL,20,Fhis body and died on 1 December.
