OL,3,CKiller who left victim to die in
OL,4,Cburning flat jailed
OL,6,FVaskouski, of Stroud Crescent East,
OL,7,FHull, was found guilty of murder after
OL,8,Fa four-week trial at Hull Crown Court.
OL,9,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,10,Fterm of 20 years.
OL,12,FDet Ch Insp Amy Keane-Christie, of
OL,13,FHumberside Police, said: "It is
OL,14,Fwithout a doubt that he is a violent
OL,15,Fand dangerous man who subjected a
OL,16,Fhelpless man to a prolonged, violent
OL,17,Fand barbaric attack."
