OL,6,FZoe Nixon, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService, added: "Mark Vaskouski left
OL,8,Fhis unconscious and fatally injured
OL,9,Fvictim in a burning building.
OL,11,F"This was the most callous and
OL,12,Fappalling crime and our thoughts
OL,13,Fremain with Tony Ibbitson's family at
OL,14,Fthis devastating time."
